data.description: PRICED BELOW APPRAISED VALUE for a swift sale! Just 15 minutes from RAFB and 20 minutes from SAMMC, this beautiful 5-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is a gem waiting to be uncovered. Boasting two spacious living areas, a large kitchen with ample cabinets and an island, a huge pantry/laundry room, and a generously sized master bedroom and bath, this property is a must-see! Ideal for those with a keen eye for potential, it's a great fixer-upper - perfect for investors or individuals looking to make it their own. FHA-203k and VA-Investment options are welcome! Don't miss this opportunity!
